data.description: This wonderful 2800 square foot home is situated in the charming Scott's Pond community. The main floor features a private master bedroom with en suite bathroom, while upstairs you'll find four spacious bedrooms. The loft area offers endless possibilities, whether you want to create a home office, a home gym, or a fun play space for the kids. The open concept kitchen overlooks the living area, making it easy to entertain during holiday events. Guests can easily move from the living room to the deck and spacious backyard. Scott's Pond is conveniently located near the interstate, hospitals, and shopping centers, making it a prime location. One of the standout features of this home is that the roof and HVAC systems have been recently updated, ensuring that all major systems are in excellent working condition. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home!
